Stanley Davis Homes is a housing Developers developer in the Yolano area, and has been a client of Cunningham Engineering Corporation. Stanley Davis developed the Davis Manor and West Manor neighborhoods in Davis. Stanley Davis Homes http://www.dcn.davis.ca.us/government/elections/s97/For_E_con.html donated $500 to the Yes on Measure E campaign in February of 1997 and partners Mitchell Betero and Ray Thompson each donated $100.

